OL,3,CWarning after elderly man scammed out
OL,4,Cof thousands on Christmas Eve
OL,6,FAn elderly man in Doncaster was
OL,7,Fscammed out of thousands of pounds on
OL,8,FChristmas Eve by fraudsters pretending
OL,9,Fto be police officers.
OL,11,FThe man, in his eighties, received a
OL,12,Fphone call from an unknown number
OL,13,Fclaiming to be a police officer in
OL,14,FDoncaster.
OL,16,FThe man was asked to help in an
OL,17,F'undercover operation' focused on
OL,18,Femployees at a local bank.
