OL,3,CWarning after elderly man scammed out
OL,4,Cof thousands on Christmas Eve
OL,6,FThe fraudster claims there is an issue
OL,7,Fwith the victim's bank account or
OL,8,Frequests the victim's help in an
OL,9,Fongoing bank or police investigation.
OL,11,FVictims are then asked to withdraw a
OL,12,Flarge sum of money which will be
OL,13,Fcollected by a courier for 'evidence'.
OL,15,FCharlotte Platts, a Fraud Protect
OL,16,FOfficer, said there are a number of
OL,17,Ftips to help spot fraudsters.
