OL,6,F"This scam can not only result in the
OL,7,Floss of significant amounts of money
OL,8,Fbut also have a real impact on the
OL,9,Fvictim's health and wellbeing. Please
OL,10,Fread these tips and keep an eye out
OL,11,Ffor any signs of courier fraud."
OL,13,FThe force issued the following tips on
OL,14,Fhow to spot fraud:
OL,16,FAnyone who believes they have been a
OL,17,Fvictim of fraud, is being urged ot
OL,18,Freport is to Action Fraud.
